==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bàn jūn rú bàn hŭ
===Etymology===
Literally: Accompanying one's sovereign can be like accompanying a tiger.
===Proverb===
'''[[伴]][[君]][[如]][[伴]][[虎]]'''
#  It can be dangerous to follow one's leader.
